HEADWORD: Denunciate
<hw>De*nun"ci*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>denuntiatus</ets>, <ets>denunciatus</ets>, p. p. of
<ets>denuntiare</ets>, <ets>-ciare</ets>. See <er>Denounce</er>.]</ety>
<def>To denounce; to condemn publicly or solemnly.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To <qex>denunciate</qex> this new work.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
